1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:14,380
Halt! No ill will I bear. I'm merely my brother's eyes and ears. I feign my loyalty to guard this path on the bear's order.

2
00:00:15,800 --> 00:00:22,280
Your destiny's bleak and stark. In its grip, we share the mark.

3
00:00:22,280 --> 00:00:29,480
The Guanyin Temple now lies in cinders, yet the elder soul endures.

4
00:00:30,640 --> 00:00:34,740
The root of greed ever fosters the stem of suffering.

5
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:43,480
Better to forget the things you truly seek.

6
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:49,560
The three bells, have you seen them all?

7
00:00:49,560 --> 00:00:49,600
No.

8
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:56,640
Do you too desire that which they ceaselessly hold dear?

